{
  "stem": "13911.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "That would be really-- So I figure I'll carry that piece of paper.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Hopefully, they'll never get to stop me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "In the meantime, I still have, like I had that [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It was called [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "That means, working shop, working shops.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "You don't say [NON-ENGLISH] in the English?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], it's French.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The working whatever, working place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [NON-ENGLISH] means, the document.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it says the city, and the date, and your name, and all this, and your-- your-- your trade.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, it's-- it's because that man knew-- knew-- knew him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, and he says, you know, they shot his wife, and he has this piece of paper.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's not that I would parade with it because it was so obvious, it cannot be me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But, it was better than nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I existed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Immediately, of course, you were supposed to live only because you are-- you have a trade.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they're were about 15 young, I would say 15, I don't-- 15, more than 10, young women in that room, knitting all day long for the Germans and their Polish girlfriends.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So you know, it was war and anything comes in handy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They brought wool, we knitted.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We even knitted pants, ski pants for their girlfriends.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Anything was good, after all.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It's Poland, and its way back, and it's-- and it's a war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We knitted caps and a lot of socks for them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, I-- I don't-- I sometimes fight to remember.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- we dreamt a lot about food, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it's funny.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe one funny thing I'll jump in with.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everybody was dreaming of food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Real food.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Oh, if we survive, if I survive, I'll have a roast beef.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If I survive, they talk.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
